## Tech Stack
- Framework: Next.js 15 with App Router. Use server components by default; add 'use client' only when needed.
- Language: TypeScript (strict mode). Use explicit prop interfaces. Never use `any`.
- Styling: Tailwind CSS v4 exclusively. No inline styles. No separate CSS files. Mobile-first responsive design.
- 3D: React Three Fiber (@react-three/fiber) and @react-three/drei. All 3D components must be client components.
- Animation: GSAP with ScrollTrigger for scroll-driven animations. Framer Motion for micro-interactions.
- Components: All reusable UI in `/components`. Page-specific components in `/components/[page-name]/`.

## Brand Colors (UCF Official)
- Primary Black: #000000 → Tailwind: `bg-ucf-black`, `text-ucf-black`
- Primary Gold: #FFC904 → Tailwind: `bg-ucf-gold`, `text-ucf-gold`
- Alt Gold: #FFCC00 → Tailwind: `bg-ucf-gold-alt`
- White: #FFFFFF → Tailwind: `bg-ucf-white`, `text-ucf-white`

## React Bits Pro
- When building hero sections, feature grids, pricing tables, stats, CTAs, navigation, or social proof sections, first check if a suitable React Bits Pro block exists at https://pro.reactbits.dev/docs/blocks/.
- Install components via: `npx shadcn@latest add @reactbits-pro/[component-name]`
- License key is in `.env.local` as `REACT_BITS_PRO_LICENSE_KEY`.

## Code Quality
- Generate complete, production-ready files. No TODOs, no placeholders, no missing logic.
- Every component must have a JSDoc comment describing its purpose and props.
- All images must use `next/image` with explicit `width`, `height`, and `alt` props.
- All links must use `next/link`.
- Ensure all pages have proper `<title>` and `<meta description>` via Next.js Metadata API.

## File Naming
- Components: PascalCase (e.g., `StadiumScene.tsx` )
- Pages: `page.tsx` inside route folders
- Utilities: camelCase (e.g., `formatDate.ts`)

## Performance
- Use `next/dynamic` with `{ ssr: false }` for all Three.js/R3F components.
- Lazy-load heavy components below the fold.
- Use `next/image` with `priority` only for above-the-fold images.